column3: I’m gonna shred you like a 20 year old tax return!
Please Kobbler, you’re nothing but a paper tiger!
The power is mine! All mine!
The other princesses will be so jealous!
Sorry Bob, but a little man like you stands no chance against a mighty warrior such as myself!
My orb! She took my orb! Where’s my orb!?
I’m getting too old for this.
